  <description><![CDATA[<p>Banff is a bustling town dominated by the majestic Cascade Mountain and offers a wealth of restaurants, shops and entertainment. Don’t miss out on the range of sightseeing and activities on offer; take a cruise on Lake Minnewanka, ride the Sulphur mountain gondola, enjoy a leisurely float trip or canoe ride along the Bow River, or ride a bike on one of the many paved trails. Be sure not to miss one of the world’s most exciting drives along the Icefields Parkway to the dazzling Colombia Icefields. To get a feel of real Canada, exchange your final 2 nights in Banff with the Guest Ranch Stay and Horseback Ride (call reservations on 01483 79 11 11 for details).</p>
<p>The final 2 nights of Banff holidays can be exchanged for one of our exciting Banff Adventure Experiences, to give you a feel of real <a href="/{localLink:6adeec13-83b7-49bb-ac73-d09144d18796}" title="Canada">Canada</a>.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
